{"tid":1811912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:已鎖定伊朗52處攻擊目標","createTime":"2020-01-05T06:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T07:41:02.000Z","uid":26331,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fee805004ed6674efeee4a375a4be80a0444a2f0","tid":1811912,"uid":26331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2346134/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2346134%2Fall&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b226f4b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2346134/all</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍上周五出動無人機空襲伊拉克首都巴格達國際機場，造成伊朗第二號人物、革命衞隊「聖城旅」(Quds Force)指揮官蘇萊馬尼(Qassem Soleimani)死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在Twitter上表示，一旦伊朗為被美軍炸死的蘇萊馬尼報仇，美國已經鎖定伊朗52處地點作為攻擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，伊朗已表明會針對美國的某些資產進行報復，他警告，如果伊朗襲擊任何美國人、或者美國資產，美國已經鎖定52個伊朗目標，其中一些對伊朗和伊朗文化非常重要，這些目標和伊朗本身都將會受到非常迅速和嚴厲的打擊。特朗普強調，美國不想要更多的威脅。"},{"pid":"47cb1e9fdfa772fb74740715561b5ce3c6723ebe","tid":1811912,"uid":153811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"金仔睇到應該龜縮左去地底"},{"pid":"0818a693d800916643976dea2a515a8c81333db8","tid":1811912,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:30:53.000Z","msg":"推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到<br />\n［停止使用建制稱呼親共人士］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQscQho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQscQho.jpg&h=56da94ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1811104</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"944a477b894f3980607c363984ec889b55500cd0","tid":1811912,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905542e196ab365fbf6f256395699a9f391a2cbd","tid":18